OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780016591
OL,3,CCanadian man will not face justice in
OL,4,CUK over alleged sale of lethal
OL,5,Csubstances
OL,7,FA Canadian man accused of selling
OL,8,Flethal substances linked to the deaths
OL,9,Fof more than 100 British people will
OL,10,Fnot face justice in the UK, the Crown
OL,11,FProsecution Service (CPS) said.
OL,13,FKenneth Law is expected to appear in
OL,14,Fcourt in Ontario, Canada, on Friday
OL,15,Faccused of aiding suicide after
OL,16,Fallegedly selling 1,200 packages
OL,17,Facross 40 countries, including the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780016591
OL,3,CCanadian man will not face justice in
OL,4,CUK over alleged sale of lethal
OL,5,Csubstances
OL,7,FAn investigation by the National Crime
OL,8,FAgency (NCA) into Canada-based
OL,9,Fwebsites selling substances to assist
OL,10,Fwith suicide found that 286
OL,11,Findividuals received packages in the
OL,12,FUK, leading to 112 deaths.
OL,14,FBut despite prosecutors in Ontario
OL,15,Fbringing Law to court, the NCA and CPS
OL,16,Fhave written to the bereaved families
OL,17,Fto tell them they would not be seeking
OL,18,Fto extradite the 60-year-old to the UK
OL,19,Fafter legal proceedings in Canada had
OL,20,Fconcluded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780016591
OL,3,CCanadian man will not face justice in
OL,4,CUK over alleged sale of lethal
OL,5,Csubstances
OL,7,FIn the letter sent on Thursday, the
OL,8,FCPS and NCA also said Canadian
OL,9,Fauthorities had confirmed that Law is
OL,10,Fexpected to plead guilty to charges of
OL,11,Faiding suicide there.
OL,13,FThe letter ` seen by the Press
OL,14,FAssociation ` stated: "After careful
OL,15,Fassessment, we agreed that Mr Law
OL,16,Fshould be sentenced for the full
OL,17,Fextent of his offending within a
OL,18,Fsingle sentencing process in Canada.
OL,19,FThis approach is not unusual in cases
OL,20,Finvolving serious offending that
OL,21,Fcrosses international borders.
OL,26,@vD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780016591
OL,3,CCanadian man will not face justice in
OL,4,CUK over alleged sale of lethal
OL,5,Csubstances
OL,7,F"We recognise that this may be painful
OL,8,Fto hear, and that some victims and
OL,9,Fbereaved families may have hoped to
OL,10,Fsee a separate prosecution in England
OL,11,Fand Wales. This difficult decision was
OL,12,Freached only after detailed
OL,13,Fconsideration of all available
OL,14,Foptions."
OL,16,FThe CPS and NCA also said in the
OL,17,Fletter it had been established that
OL,18,FLaw sent 330 products to the UK in
OL,19,Ftotal.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780016591
OL,3,CCanadian man will not face justice in
OL,4,CUK over alleged sale of lethal
OL,5,Csubstances
OL,7,FA joint statement by Joanne Jakymec,
OL,8,Fchief crown prosecutor for the CPS,
OL,9,Fand NCA deputy director Craig Turner
OL,10,Fsaid the organisations would be
OL,11,Favailable to support victims and their
OL,12,Ffamilies.
OL,14,FThe statement said: "No outcome in any
OL,15,Fcourt can remove the pain victims and
OL,16,Ftheir families have suffered. Victims
OL,17,Fhave remained our priority when making
OL,18,Fdecisions to deliver justice.
OL,26,@vD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780016591
OL,3,CCanadian man will not face justice in
OL,4,CUK over alleged sale of lethal
OL,5,Csubstances
OL,7,F"The National Crime Agency and Crown
OL,8,FProsecution Service have worked
OL,9,Fclosely with the 45 UK police forces,
OL,10,Fas well as international law
OL,11,Fenforcement, throughout the three-year
OL,12,Finvestigation.
OL,14,F"The UK is the only country globally
OL,15,Fwith an investigation detailed enough
OL,16,Fto be included in the Canadian
OL,17,Fprosecution."
OL,19,FThe families of those who died have
OL,20,Fnow called for a public inquiry.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780016591
OL,3,CCanadian man will not face justice in
OL,4,CUK over alleged sale of lethal
OL,5,Csubstances
OL,7,FThe sister of 21-year-old Aimee
OL,8,FWalton, from Southampton, who died in
OL,9,F2022, said that "doors have been shut"
OL,10,Ffor families seeking justice.
OL,12,F"If our own country will not put
OL,13,Fanyone on trial for these deaths, the
OL,14,Fvery least it can do is hold a proper
OL,15,Finquiry into how they were allowed to
OL,16,Fhappen."
OL,26,@qD@QOUqD@fO]tD@AOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780016591
OL,3,CCanadian man will not face justice in
OL,4,CUK over alleged sale of lethal
OL,5,Csubstances
OL,7,FAdele Zeynep Walton said: "The
OL,8,Fquestion for our own country is
OL,9,Fsimpler still: who here will examine
OL,10,Fhow the British state let this happen,
OL,11,Fand what it will do so that no other
OL,12,Ffamily goes through it?
OL,14,F"A foreign sentencing hearing cannot
OL,15,Fanswer that. Only a statutory public
OL,16,Finquiry can."
OL,26,@oD@[OUvD@AOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
