PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1780016591
OL,3,CCanadian man will not face justice in
OL,4,CUK over alleged sale of lethal
OL,5,Csubstances
OL,7,FAndy Burrows, chief executive of Molly
OL,8,FRose Foundation, said: "Bereaved
OL,9,Ffamilies have been campaigning
OL,10,Ftirelessly to hold Kenneth Law to
OL,11,Faccount in the UK and to be told he
OL,12,Fwill not be prosecuted here on the eve
OL,13,Fof his court case in Canada is a
OL,14,Fbitter blow.
OL,16,F"Families up and down the country have
OL,17,Fbeen impacted by Law's crimes and
OL,18,Fshould have the right to full justice
OL,19,Fin the UK.
OL,26,@pD@XOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
