OL,3,CCanadian man will not face justice in
OL,4,CUK over alleged sale of lethal
OL,5,Csubstances
OL,7,F"As long as the pro-suicide forum
OL,8,Fremains online, and while this
OL,9,Fsubstance is available in the UK and
OL,10,Facross borders, more vulnerable people
OL,11,Fare at risk."
OL,13,F` Call Samaritans for free on 116 123,
OL,14,Femail jo@samaritans.org or visit
OL,15,Fsamaritans.org for more information.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@MO]
